### Overview
This file defines the `ToolWrapper` static class that builds a dictionary of executable tool functions from a registry of `ToolSpec` definitions. It handles JSON argument parsing, required parameter validation, destructive action confirmation, signed-file policy normalization, fetch host allowlisting, and result serialization.

